Package: limiric
Title: Damaged Cell Detection for Single Cell RNA Sequencing Quality Control
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alicen", "Henning", email = "alicen.jhb@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: 
    A quality control tool for single cell RNA sequencing that enables
    high precision, sample-specific damaged cell detection through 
    low-dimension mitochondrial and ribosomal cluster selection.
